basisset.dc:title: jul-cc-pV(Q+d)Z
basisset.dc:description: jul-cc-pV(Q+d)Z basis set is a trimmed version of the aug-cc-pV(Q+d)Z basis set of Dunning and coworkers. It is obtained by augmenting the cc-pV(Q+d)Z basis set with only s, p, d, f, and g diffuse functions on the heavy (Li and up) atoms. No diffuse functions are used on H and He atoms.
